quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First of all, make an effort to move east. Following that, head south. Then, make an effort to move west. Then, attempt to venture west. After that, make an attempt to go to the west. With that over with, make an effort to travel north. And then, take a trip north. Then, attempt to move east. Then, pick up the sponge from the counter inside the laundry place. After taking the sponge, throw the sponge on the floor of the laundry place. And once you've done that, you win!
